## Two Models

| | Essence | Expression |
|---|---|---|
| Compute | CPU only | NVIDIA GPU or Apple Silicon M3+ |
| Avatar source | Pre-built `.imx` file | Any face image at runtime |
| Gestures | Yes | No |
| Identity swap | No | Yes (`set_identity()`) |
| Best for | Kiosks, edge, 24/7 | Custom faces, native apps |

## Pricing

| Model | Self-hosted | Cloud |
|---|---|---|
| Essence | 1 cr/min | 2 cr/min |
| Expression | 2 cr/min | 4 cr/min |
| Agent generation | 250 cr one-time | -- |
| Free tier | 99 cr/month | -- |

