## Mistakes to Avoid

- Do not reference private repos (`bithuman-kit`, `bithuman-product/platform`).
- Do not hardcode API secrets. Use environment variables.
- Do not use `figure_id` (deprecated). Use `agent_code`.
- Do not pin Swift SDK below 0.8.1.
- Do not try to run Expression models on CPU -- they need GPU or M3+.
- Do not poll `/v1/agent/status/` faster than every 5 seconds.
- Do not import from `bithuman.internal` or undocumented modules.
